title: Kyle Sangster
text:
Investor and trader, philosophical rascal, co-owner and co-founder of TradingMunks, an investment and financial technology enterprise. By training and profession, I’m either a computer scientist or software developer. Outside work, I’m an avid reader, travel junkie, and practitioner of the Eastern arts.
On this site I keep a list of projects, my resume, and a blog about intellectual, technical and curious pursuits.
